David,
Why not just add a flag for a VMA telling if you want / do not want to
copy it on "fork()" ? E.g.:
dup_mmap():
	for (= current->mm->mmap ; mpnt ; mpnt = mpnt->vm_next) {
		if (mpnt->vm_flags & VM_HUGETLB_DONT_COPY)
			<do nothing>
	}
Regards,
Zoltán Menyhárt
